Description: scRNAseqPlants provides filtered and unfiltered matrices for gene-level counts(exons) as well as velocyto counts(spliced, unspiced, and ambiguous) as SingleCellExperiment objects. Essential Sample-level metadata is also included for any level of re-analysis.  
